## Performance Impact Assessment

**Current Implementation**:
- ⚠️ O(n) regex scan on every keystroke (n = document length before cursor)
- ⚠️ No debouncing despite `activateOnTyping: true`
- ⚠️ Global regex matches (line 129) scan entire document

**Recommended Improvements**:
1. Add `activateOnTypingDelay: 200` to autocomplete config ([source](https://github.com/codemirror/autocomplete))
2. Limit context scanning to last 500 characters
3. Return `null` early for non-explicit triggers on structural characters

